= Remove Fear =
'''Sphere:''' Special  
'''Level:''' 1  
'''Range:''' 30 yds  
'''Components:''' V, S, M (cross or holy water)  
'''Duration:''' 1 turn  
'''Casting Time:''' 1 turn  
'''Area of Effect:''' 1 creature per level  
'''Saving Throw:''' None  

== Description ==
Counters magical and non-magical fear. Grants new saving throw with +1 bonus or removes ongoing fear.

== Special Notes ==
* Treated as a [[Prayer]] in this campaign.
* All casting times and durations are increased by an order of magnitude (round → turn, turn → hour, etc).
* Requires cross and/or holy water.
